text: Collin Ray Williams (1 November 1961 - 24 April 2022) was a Zimbabwean cricketer who played five first class matches and one list A cricket match for Matabeleland. He also coached Zimbabwe hockey team. He was the father of Zimbabwean cricketer Sean Williams. He was born in Bulawayo, Zimbabwe. Williams died on 24 April 2022 in Bulawayo at the age of 60. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1961 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Zimbabwean cricketers
